# Plugin manifests, skills, and commands must use LF line endings.
# Claude Code's frontmatter parser matches the `---` delimiter exactly;
# a trailing CR (CRLF) breaks frontmatter parsing and the skill/command
# fails to load. Pin these to LF regardless of platform or core.autocrlf.
*.md           text eol=lf
*.json         text eol=lf
**/SKILL.md    text eol=lf
**/commands/*  text eol=lf
